description:
My HoneyDew this week is Chelsea Skidmore! Chelsea highlights lowlights about addiction, her time as a stripper (where a couple of her dad’s friends caught her) and three nights of drinking after a bad breakup that caused her to relapse which resulted in a rehab visit/suicide attempt/5150!
